(719, 'There is nothing we can do to stop the Americans from destroying Cuba, other than surrender, which is unthinkable', 'EX VBZ NN PRP MD VB TO VB DT NNPS IN VBG NNP JJ IN NN WDT VBZ JJ', '1,10,14,8', NULL),
